PREFIX cc: <http://creativecommons.org/ns#>

PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>

PREFIX yago: <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/>

  ?mountain a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Mountain> .
  {
    ?mountain <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/locatedInArea> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany> .
  }

}

  BIND(xsd:integer(SUBSTR(STR(?beginyearRaw), 1, 4)) AS ?beginyear) .
  BIND(xsd:integer(SUBSTR(STR(?endyearRaw), 1, 4)) AS ?endyear) .

}

SELECT DISTINCT ?library WHERE {

  {
    ?library <http://dbpedia.org/property/established> ?established .
    FILTER (datatype(?established) = xsd:integer || datatype(?established) = xsd:decimal || !bound(datatype(?established))) .

}
